imdb.title: Ask That Guy with the Glasses
akas: Ask That Guy with the Glasses (United States)
plot: A reserved sociopath answers very bizarre questions and gives equally or even more bizarre answers.::Anonymous
synopsis: Viewers submit questions, some normal and some downright insane, and That Guy with the Glasses, an eccentric, all-knowing young man who has a particularly dark sense of humor and a quite perverted nature. No question is too disturbing or above answering.
